---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'

// Privacy policy last updated date
const lastUpdated = 'August 9, 2025'
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Japan Travel Journal"
  description="Privacy Policy for Japan Travel Journal. Learn about our Cookie usage, Google AdSense, Google Analytics and data collection practices."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>Japan Travel Log (hereinafter referred to as "this site") is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>For the purposes of improving our services and delivering advertisements, we may automatically collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>Date and time of access</li>
            <li>Pages viewed and referring URLs</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. Use of Cookies</h2>
          <p>This site uses cookies to enhance user experience and display relevant advertisements.<br>
          You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features of the site may not function properly.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. About Google AdSense</h2>
          <p>We use Google AdSense, a service provided by Google, to display advertisements.<br>
          Google and its partners use cookies to serve ads based on your interests and previous visits to this site or other websites.<br>
          For more details, please refer to the Google Policies and Terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Analytics Tools</h2>
          <p>This site uses Google Analytics to analyze website usage.<br>
          Google Analytics uses cookies, but the data collected does not include personally identifiable information.<br>
          For more information, please see the Google Privacy Policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Provision to Third Parties</h2>
          <p>We do not provide personal information to third parties without the user's consent, except as required by law.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>We make no guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of the content on this site.<br>
          We are not responsible for any damages resulting from the use of this site.<br>
          We also assume no responsibility for the content or privacy practices of external sites linked from this site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy when necessary.<br>
          Any changes will take effect when posted on this page.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-800 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <p><strong>Operator:</strong> Hide</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> yamazaki2357@gmail.com</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Privacy policy specific styles */
  .prose h2 {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose a {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .prose a:hover {
    color: #1d4ed8;
  }
  
  .prose ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>